 :15 - Friday 12 June 2026 17:15\n\nEnergetic genre-scrambling groove-machi
 ne\n\nDutch collective YĪN YĪN scramble global movements in a blender:
  psych rock\, Thai funk\, Japanese city pop... anything that tickles their
  current fancy.\nTheir omnivorous spirit often unfolds in some of the most
  succulent grooves imaginable\, with a vibrant assembly of traditional ins
 truments\, vintage synths and flavorful percussion spicing everything up. 
 YĪN YĪN have truly perfected the art of musical fusion cooking.\n\nArt
 ist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/yin-yin\nSchedule source: 
 https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/friday/schedule
