 :30 - Saturday 13 June 2026 00:00\n\nRock music's chief anti-hero\n\nA leg
 endary guitar hero in days where that concept seems rarer and rarer\, Jack
  White never plays it safe.\nWith so many iconic rock songs under his name
 \, many would have settled the course. Yet White stubbornly keeps going ag
 ainst the grain as a sonic iconoclast\, tender of timeless songcraft and l
 abel owner of Third Man Records. Qualities steadily upheld in his own exte
 nsive solo output\, and in bands like The White Stripes\, The Dead Weather
  and The Raconteurs. And everyone knows about it.\n\nArtist source: https:
 //www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/jack-white\nSchedule source: https://www.bes
 tkeptsecret.nl/program/friday/schedule
