 2026 22:00 - Friday 12 June 2026 23:00\n\nInfectious Afrobeats cult hero\n
 \nAta Kak’s rise as cult phenomenon shows us the power of Doing It Yours
 elf – how it can cultivate some completely original pop music. Yaw Atta-
 Owusu knew he liked reggae music\, he liked funk\, he liked Ghanaian high 
 life music\, and he liked Grandmaster Flash. But why pick just one? With t
 he necessary recording equipment\, his signature Twi flow and an unblemish
 ed zest for life\, Ata Kak’s legendary LP Obaa Sima became a global gras
 sroots success. And we're still dancing feverishly to its tunes today.\n\n
 Artist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/ata-kak\nSchedule sourc
