  happen\n\nDJ St. Paul aka the pundit behind Pop-O-Matic\, aka the honcho 
 of Let It Happen\, aka the chief facilitator of Best Kept Secret's The Flo
 or.Paul isn’t a floor manager like those at normal work environments\; i
 t’s all play in his book. Every year he invites an uncanny list of guest
 s from all corners and crevices of the music world – blasting the bigges
 t hits\, the most vital niches & subcultures\, the juiciest of deep cuts\,
  and everything inbetween at The Floor. It’s quite literally all hands o
 n deck when St. Paul’s your host – an exploration of pure dance-floor 
 euphoria in all its vast deviations. An individual eternally ready for bot
 h the moment and the sound.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.n
