 2026 16:45 - Friday 12 June 2026 17:30\n\nPure-hearted\, cheeky garage ban
 gers\n\nA good riff\, a good hook and pure attitude: Buenos Aires garage-d
 uo Pacifica are the definition of no-frills cool.\nIndeed\, the winds defi
 nitely worked in Inés Adam and Martina Nintzel’s favour when a random i
 nternet commenter – and a mutual appreciation for The Strokes – brough
 t them together to form a band. The duo’s combined brilliance forges ear
 worms that illustrate the messier aspects of being young\, in love with li
 fe and coping with all the treacherous growing pains that come with that. 
 Pacifica are fun\, frantic and utterly in-your-face.\n\nArtist source: htt
 ps://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/pacifica\nSchedule source: https://www.be
 stkeptsecret.nl/program/friday/schedule
