 ap and theatre\n\nUnder her rapper alter ego Elmer\, Dutch artist & produc
 er Merel Pauw is a bona fide interloper\, causing shockwaves within the di
 scourse of theatre\, hip-hop and pop.On debut album ‘platland’\, Elmer
  forges a vital and off-beat mix of rap\, techno and cabaret: a musical jo
 urney swerving between playful agitation and deep reflection. Elmer’s sh
 ows celebrate the weird and pull against the threads of gender roles and n
 ormative thinking with inventive (musical) contrasts and witty lyricism. A
  true cultural tour-de-force.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret
