 e 2026 00:15 - Saturday 13 June 2026 01:00\n\nCatchy & distinctive genre-b
 lender with DIY-ethos\n\nUS artist Frankie Beanie's ground rules for his s
 olo-project supermodel*: don't try and be cool\, nick everything\, keep it
  lowercase\, don't overthink\, always talk about fight club. It translates
  to fun\, thrifty songs that channel MF Doom as much as LCD Soundsystem. B
 eanie’s frank\, observational lyrics draw partly from his experiences as
  an American living in the UK\, complete with Be Kind Rewind-esque homages
  to Jamiroquai and Fatboy Slim. Effortlessly charming\, unpolished and yea
 h\, actually pretty damn cool.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecre
 t.nl/bands/supermodel\nSchedule source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/prog
 ram/friday/schedule
