DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Secret\nTime: Saturday 13 Jun
 e 2026 21:30 - Saturday 13 June 2026 22:30\n\nRapturous Gogo spirituals\n\
 nTanzania's Zawose Queens channel vibrations of the ancestors through thei
 r rapturous polyphonic singing. As the daughter and granddaughter of the l
 egendary Dr. Hukwe Zawose\, Leah and Pendo are ushering in the family trad
 ition as its first female practitioners. Their fusion of the Gogo music an
 d modern-day electronics expresses a deep connection towards nature\, to c
 eremony and to ritual: music teeming with unshakable spirit and fire.\n\nA
 rtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/the-zawose-queens\nSched
 ule source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
