SUMMARY:BCUC
LOCATION:The Secret
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Secret\nTime: Saturday 13 Jun
 e 2026 23:30 - Sunday 14 June 2026 00:30\n\nFast & furious Afro-psych jams
 \n\nThe Afropsychedelic pounce of Bantu Continua Uhuru Consciousness screa
 ms with a zealous\, ceremonial spirit.BCUC's formula seems so simple when 
 you break it down: bass\, drums\, percussion\, voice chants all conspiring
  to spark frantic\, joyous movement. And the Soweto\, South-Africa based c
 ollective does this better than anyone: this is music awakened from ancien
 t lineage\, yet visionary\, loud and transcending convention of what a ban
 d can be.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/bcuc\nSche
 dule source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
