DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Secret\nTime: Sunday 14 June 
 2026 01:30 - Sunday 14 June 2026 04:00\n\nGenre-blending DJ who brings tha
 t rare dancefloor euphoria\n\nIf one is forced to narrow down a Lucky Done
  Gone DJ set in just two terms\, it would be ‘carefree and contagious’
 .\nAnd if a third signifier can be cheated in\, you can add 'genre-blurrin
 g' to the mix as well. Like a magpie who loves all shiny things\, Lucky ch
 errypicks his favorite elements from basically any imaginable club movemen
 t – be it house\, 90s techno\, 00s trance\, old school or new school –
  and mold it into something fresh and euphoria-inducing. A master at his c
 raft\, passion and proficiency personified.\n\nArtist source: https://www.
 bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/lucky-done-gone\nSchedule source: https://www.best
 keptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
