  2026 12:00 - Saturday 13 June 2026 13:30\n\nThe Floor manager who lets it
  all happen\n\nDJ St. Paul aka the pundit behind Pop-O-Matic\, aka the hon
 cho of Let It Happen\, aka the chief facilitator of Best Kept Secret's The
  Floor.Paul isn’t a floor manager like those at normal work environments
 \; it’s all play in his book. Every year he invites an uncanny list of g
 uests from all corners and crevices of the music world – blasting the bi
 ggest hits\, the most vital niches & subcultures\, the juiciest of deep cu
 ts\, and everything inbetween at The Floor. It’s quite literally all han
 ds on deck when St. Paul’s your host – an exploration of pure dance-fl
 oor euphoria in all its vast deviations. An individual eternally ready for
  both the moment and the sound.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecr
 et.nl/bands/dj-st-paul\nSchedule source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/pro
 gram/saturday/schedule
