SUMMARY:Katayoun
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Floor\nTime: Saturday 13 June
  2026 13:30 - Saturday 13 June 2026 14:30\n\nCollector\, radio host & DJ o
 f Iranian music\n\nKatayoun Arian is a DJ\, selector and archivist working
  across sounds from Iran and the wider region.\nDrawing on everything from
  pre-revolution grooves and pop to trance-inducing ritual rhythms\, she bu
 ilds sets that cut across borders and timelines. Her work moves between de
 eper listening and dancefloor: it is less about nostalgia\, more about the
  reactivation of rarities and bringing together different musical worlds\,
  showing how music can move beyond boundaries.\nPhoto by: Lisa van den Ber
 g\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/katayoun\nSchedule
  source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
