SUMMARY:Ko Kliko
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Floor\nTime: Saturday 13 June
  2026 18:00 - Saturday 13 June 2026 19:00\n\nElectronic indie crusader on 
 a mission\n\nKo Kliko stands for postpunk\, electroclash\, indie\, alterna
 tive pop and trends that can go right in the trashcan.\nIf it is up to Cor
 a Ziengs\, genres are boring. She even has a successful alter ego playing 
 house and jazz (Coco Coquelicot). The passionate DJ is one of the founders
  of Relate Radio\, a stalwart within the Music scene of Groningen and has 
 made her way to festivals like ESNS and Lowlands. Not by giving in\, but b
 y lashing out. The Floor can only approve\n\nArtist source: https://www.be
 stkeptsecret.nl/bands/ko-kliko\nSchedule source: https://www.bestkeptsecre
 t.nl/program/saturday/schedule
