SUMMARY:Ineffekt
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Floor\nTime: Saturday 13 June
  2026 21:00 - Saturday 13 June 2026 22:00\n\nBass-heavy but light-hearted 
 producer on the rise\n\nMasterful Dutch producer gaining international mom
 entum with his bass-heavy but light-hearted sound.\nAfter Sammy Virji and 
 MEGRA before him\, this years UK Bass inspired golden hour at The Floor wi
 ll go to our own Ineffekt. His tracks are frequently supported by producer
 s like Four Tet and platforms such as the BBC\, but are just as easily the
  main ingredient for eclectic DJ’s like host DJ St. Paul who couldn’t 
 be more proud to present this true gem of an artist. More than an icon. At
  the exact heart of the festival this will be the soundtrack to your new f
 ound hopes and dreams. No refund for lost chagrin!\n\nArtist source: https
 ://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/ineffekt\nSchedule source: https://www.best
 keptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
