 026 01:00 - Sunday 14 June 2026 02:00\n\nCelebrating organic sounds in a d
 ystopian world\n\nAjuma understands the power of music to evoke emotions l
 ike no other.\nShe’s an ardent music lover with an ear for the surprisin
 g and obscure. Wherever she goes\, she leaves behind a warm and inviting a
 tmosphere on the dancefloor\, blending together genres into a recognizable
  sound that is always soulful oriented. She moves between deeper and uplif
 ting moments\, at the heart of her sound lies an endless love for that (ra
 w) percussion. Ajuma is opening borders. Surrender your love!\n\nArtist so
 urce: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/ajuma\nSchedule source: https://
 www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
