SUMMARY:The Great Indie Dance Bake Off (DJ St. Paul B2B Riptide)
LOCATION:The Floor
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Floor\nTime: Sunday 14 June 2
 026 02:00 - Sunday 14 June 2026 04:00\n\nGifted producer and passionate Fl
 oor-manager breaking down the history of indie dance\n\nI was there! Produ
 cer Riptide and host DJ St. Paul present the premiere of The Great Indie D
 ance Bake Off.The finale of Saturday night at the Floor has a tradition of
  memorable B2Bs. This time producer Riptide (his Rug Busters remix for Per
 sonal Trainer is what Charli would call a modern-day club classic) and DJ 
 St. Paul will take you on an colourful journey through the history of indi
 e dance. Travelling from Talking Heads via Gorillaz to Decius and Robyn. P
 remiering some of their own edits of favourite tracks. Oh\, if I could see
  all my friends tonight!\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/b
 ands/the-great-indie-dance-bake-off-dj-st-paul-b2b-riptide\nSchedule sourc
 e: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
