SUMMARY:Bruno Berle
LOCATION:The Casbah
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Casbah\nTime: Saturday 13 Jun
 e 2026 12:15 - Saturday 13 June 2026 13:00\n\nSupple polaroid filter latin
  pop\n\nThis Brazilian composer and troubadour writes honeysweet latin pop
  brimming with deft arrangements.\nFrom accounts of people who have been t
 o Brazil\, it does seem like time works differently over there. Bruno Berl
 e’s warm-blooded pop affirms this notion all the more. Carefree\, soft a
 round the edges and unhurried\, Berle’s tunes embrace you with the kind 
 of affinity of a home-cooked meal. For you lovers out there\, Bruno’s se
 t at Best Kept would be good time to get cosy.\n\nArtist source: https://w
 ww.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/bruno-berle\nSchedule source: https://www.bestk
 eptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
