DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Casbah\nTime: Saturday 13 Jun
 e 2026 13:45 - Saturday 13 June 2026 14:30\n\nJangly indie pop sensation\n
 \nAfter breaking out with their sun-kissed open-the-drapes single 'Snug Ba
 rber'\, this Aussie five-piece is immediately irresistable.\nMaintaining a
  fine-tuned balance between jangly and cinematic\, Any Young Mechanic reca
 ll Vampire Weekend or perhaps a slightly more mellowed out Violent Femmes.
  They embody the comfort of a frayed sweater\, with an affable\, somewhat 
 neurotic charm.\n\nArtist source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/any-
 young-mechanic\nSchedule source: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/sat
 urday/schedule
