SUMMARY:Grote Geelstaart
LOCATION:The Casbah
DESCRIPTION:Best Kept Secret 2026 test import - shifted 1 day earlier\nStage: The Casbah\nTime: Saturday 13 Jun
 e 2026 15:15 - Saturday 13 June 2026 16:00\n\nMath-tastic prog-noise minio
 ns\n\nImagine Geordie Greep fronting Talking Heads instead of David Byrne:
  that's just one wild take on the baffling madness of rising Dutch outfit 
 Grote Geelstaart.\nIf music was somehow a math equation unlocking the fift
 h dimension in space\, Grote Geelstaart are the kind of band to figure it 
 out\, using odd time signatures\, riffs that scream 'fuck you\, diatonic s
 cale!'\, and a lot of sweating it out through three-piece suits. Grote Gee
 lstaart's music will flop like fish out of water\, only to magically grow 
 arms and legs on the spot: rock music evolving in real time!\n\nArtist sou
 rce: https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/bands/grote-geelstaart\nSchedule source
 : https://www.bestkeptsecret.nl/program/saturday/schedule
