 tronics\n\nApichat Pakwan brings a lively crossover of electronics and Tha
 i esan and molam movements: the sweetest balance between the modern and th
 e traditional.It unfolds miraculously live as well: you have producer Oliv
 ier Schreuder serving up beats that blend seamlessly with the Thai musicia
 ns and singers: not in that crude mash-up kind of way\, but warmly courtin
 g each other in a tryst. This approach carries over to audiences\, creatin
 g a hot & sweltering dancefloor environment.\n\nArtist source: https://www
